data.description: Seller is willing to negotiate the options of buying the buyers rate down and paying closing cost. Lovely single story, three bedroom, two bath with two car garage in the desirable Wynwood subdivision! Open floor plan, living, family room and two eating areas. Large kitchen with smooth cooktop, built in microwaves and breakfast bar. Step into the nice master bedroom with full bath to include double vanity, garden tub and separate shower. The secondary bedrooms provide ample space. Relax and take in the evening with the covered porch, deck and above ground pool! The outside HVAC unit was replaced in January 2023 and inside unit replaced two years ago. Close to Lackland AFB, shopping, restaurants and tons of entertainment!
